Description_lang: The Stygian Abductor unleashes chains at their target and all players within $A1 yards, inflicting $s3 Shadow damage divided evenly among all players struck.In addition, the Abductor begins to pull each hit target off the platform. The force of this effect is reduced by the number of players being chained. After struggling for $d, the Abductor is pulled from the skies.
AuraDescription_lang: Being dragged by a Stygian Abductor.
